ransformation  and r n      workforce development  Training and education include projects on consumer r n      leadership development  client self advocacy  peer provider certification  r n      financial asset development  preparing for research careers  and inpatient r n      seclusion and restraint reduction An innovative academic curricular transformation effort incorporates principles r n      of recovery and evidence based practice into university instruction in r n      the medical  social  and behavioral sciences  Also offered are online workshops  r n      web casts  web based continuing education courses  and a state of the science national summit held in  April      national summit APA Press Release on Center s WRAP Research  APA Press Release on Center s WRAP Research  Online support group study for mothers with a psychiatric disability Online support group study for mothers with a psychiatric disability Explore our recent research Explore our recent research NEW One Stop Source  for Information on MH Self Directed Care NEW One Stop Source  for Information on MH Self Directed Care Latest Findings on WRAP as Evidence Based Practice n Abstract   n PDF   n Full Text    Abstract    PDF    Full Text   Financial Ed Curriculum Now Available for Download Financial Ed Curriculum Now Available for Download Free Cultural Competency Guidebook and Assessment Tool for  Peer Run Programs and Self Help Groups Free Cultural Competency Guidebook and Assessment Tool for  Peer Run Programs and Self Help Groups New Report on Asset Development for People in Mental Health Recovery New Report on Asset Development for People in Mental Health Recovery Self Determination  The Fierce Urgency of Now r n  An Invitational State of the Science Summit Self Determination  The Fierce Urgency of Now r n  An Invitational State of the Science Summit New Webcast  Evidence New Webcast  Evidence New Webcast  "Promoting r nMental Health Recovery Through Evidence Based Supported Employment Promo